<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Robotics Inventory - Home</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>

<body>
  <%- include("./partials/header", {active:"home"}) %>
    <div class="content-container hero-container">
      <div class="hero">
        <div class="info">
          <div class="title">Robotics Inventory</div>
          <div class="graphic">
            <img src="/hero-graphic.svg" alt="Hero Graphic">
          </div>
          <div class="subtext">Your one-stop electronics tracking application.</div>
          <a class="explore-button" href="/categories">
            Explore
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="graphic">
          <img src="/hero-graphic.svg" alt="Hero Graphic">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content-container">
      <div class="usefulness-section">
        <div class="section-title">How to use it?</div>
        <div class="cards-grid">
          <div class="card">
            <div class="title">Browse Categories</div>
            <div class="subtext">View all robotics component categories and explore items grouped by type.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="title">Add or Edit Components</div>
            <div class="subtext">Create new components or update existing ones to practice open CRUD operations.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="title">Search & Filter</div>
            <div class="subtext">Quickly find components using name-based search and category filtering.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="title">Data Protection</div>
            <div class="subtext">Deletion is intentionally restricted to protect shared data in an open system.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-container">
      <div class="technical-section">
        <div class="section-title">Technical Overview</div>
        <div class="cards-grid">
          <div class="card">
            <div class="title">Architecture</div>
            <ul>
              <li>Server-rendered web application using Express and EJS</li>
              <li>RESTful routing for categories and components</li>
              <li>PostgreSQL relational database for structured data</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="title">Backend Concepts</div>
            <ul>
              <li>CRUD operations for related categories and components</li>
              <li>Validation and error handling for incoming user data</li>
              <li>Query-based search and filtering via request parameters</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-container">
      <div class="footer">
        <div class="black-line"></div>
        <div class="text">© 2026 <a href="https://github.com/whatisaProCoder">whatisaProCoder</a>. All rights reserved.
        </div>
        <div class="black-line"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>